33:03.716 --> 33:06.416
Unfortunately, a lot of people
confuse witchcraft

33:06.418 --> 33:10.220
with the fictional caricatures
they see on TV and in novels.

33:10.222 --> 33:12.522
<i>This is quite clearly
one of the reasons</i>

33:12.524 --> 33:15.025
<i>most people disbelieve
in the supernatural.</i>

33:15.027 --> 33:17.294
<i>But the truth
is that witches do exist,</i>

33:17.296 --> 33:18.829
<i>as does magic.</i>

33:18.831 --> 33:21.898
<i>And like all things in life,
magic could be used for good</i>

33:21.900 --> 33:23.233
<i>or it could be used for evil.</i>

33:23.235 --> 33:26.436
<i>Black magic spells
bring death and destruction.</i>

33:26.438 --> 33:28.672
White magic spells
bring healing.

33:28.674 --> 33:30.440
<i>A greatly experienced witch,</i>

33:30.442 --> 33:32.342
<i>which is a high priest
or priestess,</i>

33:32.344 --> 33:34.511
can cast the most
powerful of spells,

33:34.513 --> 33:36.980
even on some
very rare occasions,

33:36.982 --> 33:40.550
<i>a resurrection spell
which can bring back the dead.</i>

33:40.552 --> 33:41.718
But one must understand

33:41.720 --> 33:44.388
that the universe's life force
is limited.

33:44.390 --> 33:46.790
It must be taken
from other living things

33:46.792 --> 33:49.259
and only the most
experienced casters

33:49.261 --> 33:52.496
are able to control where
that life force is taken from.

33:52.498 --> 33:54.865
<i>So it is imperative
that these spells</i>

33:54.867 --> 33:57.200
<i>are only performed
by the right people</i>

33:57.202 --> 33:58.201
<i>for the right reasons.</i>

33:59.738 --> 34:03.106
Hey, I, uh,
just talked to Sheriff.

34:03.108 --> 34:05.208
He's gonna send
one of his deputies over

34:05.210 --> 34:07.344
to watch out for us.

34:07.346 --> 34:08.745
- That's good to know.
- Yep.

34:11.984 --> 34:14.851
Okay, honey, then
I'll just leave you to it.

34:30.569 --> 34:32.903
Hello. Rebecca.
It's very nice to meet you.

34:32.905 --> 34:35.072
Hi. It's nice to meet you too.

34:35.074 --> 34:38.175
Um, thank you so much
for getting back to me.

34:38.177 --> 34:39.076
<i>It's my pleasure.</i>

34:39.078 --> 34:41.411
I, I see that you live
in the Napa Valley.

34:41.413 --> 34:43.747
It's a very beautiful place
to live.

34:43.749 --> 34:47.217
<i>One of my dearest friends
lives in that area too.</i>

34:47.219 --> 34:49.086
What can I do to help you?

34:49.088 --> 34:53.723
Well, I really enjoyed
your video on witchcraft,

34:53.725 --> 34:57.694
and it really inspired me
to want to meet a witch.

34:58.897 --> 35:00.931
Look, this might
sound ridiculous,

35:00.933 --> 35:04.201
but do you know
any real witches?

35:04.803 --> 35:06.036
Because if you do,

35:06.038 --> 35:08.405
then I could
really use their help.

35:08.407 --> 35:10.507
That is an excellent question.

35:10.509 --> 35:14.311
And it is highly probable
that I do know of a real witch.

35:14.313 --> 35:15.912
<i>But it's just not
the kind of information</i>

35:15.914 --> 35:17.414
<i>I give out to just anyone,
willy-nilly.</i>

35:17.416 --> 35:20.784
I'd have to ask you
a whole multitude of questions

35:20.786 --> 35:23.720
just to set up an appointment
with someone like that.

35:23.722 --> 35:25.455
Incidentally...

35:25.457 --> 35:28.692
When we were actually thinking
of meeting this real witch?

35:28.694 --> 35:32.062
Tonight, if possible.
It's very urgent.

35:32.064 --> 35:34.431
<i>Look, please, I'm not trying
to waste your time.</i>

35:34.433 --> 35:36.633
I'll pay you if I need to.

35:36.635 --> 35:39.536
This is very important to me.

35:39.538 --> 35:42.973
Hmm, I think I might know
just the right person for you.

35:42.975 --> 35:44.541
But before we can proceed,

35:44.543 --> 35:48.178
I'm gonna have to ask you
some very detailed questions.

35:48.180 --> 35:50.180
<i>Of course,
I'll answer anything.</i>

35:50.182 --> 35:52.115
<i>Just tell me
what you need to know.</i>

35:56.321 --> 35:58.722
If we don't find this place
in the next five minutes,

35:58.724 --> 35:59.956
we're heading back.

35:59.958 --> 36:02.325
We should be there any minute.

36:02.327 --> 36:03.760
Take a left up here.

36:04.930 --> 36:09.032
Rebecca,
I really don't like this.

36:09.034 --> 36:12.002
Are you sure you have
to talk to a witch priestess?

36:12.738 --> 36:15.839
I just want some answers.

36:15.841 --> 36:17.574
Can't hurt to talk to her, Dad.

36:17.576 --> 36:21.178
All right. But I'm telling you,
it's a complete waste of time.

36:21.180 --> 36:24.848
It's like those TV psychics.
It's fucking rip off.

36:24.850 --> 36:27.050
Okay, it's going to be
right up here on the left.

36:28.487 --> 36:29.553
Yeah, right here.

36:50.309 --> 36:51.508
Rebecca.

36:51.510 --> 36:53.610
- Yeah.
- Nice to meet you.

36:53.612 --> 36:55.412
- Nice to meet you.
- Please come in.

36:55.414 --> 36:56.479
Okay.

37:01.920 --> 37:06.022
It can be done,
but I rarely recommend it.

37:07.693 --> 37:09.859
When you bring back the dead,

37:09.861 --> 37:13.263
they might not come back
the person they once were.

37:13.265 --> 37:16.166
There can be
very negative consequences,

37:16.168 --> 37:19.970
especially if that person
doesn't want to be resurrected.

37:21.907 --> 37:25.375
- Are you sure you wanna do this?
- Yes.

37:25.377 --> 37:28.778
Yes, I'm sure.
Mark meant everything to me.

37:28.780 --> 37:31.147
I would do anything
to be with him again.

37:32.351 --> 37:34.484
Please, I beg you.

37:34.486 --> 37:36.052
Help me bring him back.

37:41.093 --> 37:44.427
Henrik and his followers
are using magic

37:44.429 --> 37:46.062
for all the wrong reasons.

37:48.033 --> 37:51.101
Magic is meant to help people,
not destroy them.

37:57.776 --> 37:59.876
I will revive Mark for you...

38:01.913 --> 38:05.348
because I sense that your heart
is in the right place.

38:05.350 --> 38:06.283
Thank you.

38:09.087 --> 38:11.621
Love is something
no evil can take away.

38:12.924 --> 38:14.724
Now keep in mind,

38:14.726 --> 38:17.127
what we will be doing
is illegal,

38:17.996 --> 38:20.263
some would say immoral.

38:20.265 --> 38:23.199
I need you to go home
and really think about this.

38:23.201 --> 38:25.635
If you decide
to go through with it,

38:25.637 --> 38:26.970
you let me know.

38:28.507 --> 38:29.639
But, Rebecca,

38:32.110 --> 38:34.944
no one can know about this.

38:35.314 --> 38:36.379
No one.

38:37.616 --> 38:38.548
Okay.

38:43.522 --> 38:44.954
Okay. Bye.

38:46.792 --> 38:48.091
So how'd it go?

38:48.093 --> 38:49.526
Is she a kook or what?

38:49.528 --> 38:51.094
No, she's very helpful.

39:34.606 --> 39:35.638
Mornin', Dad.

39:36.908 --> 39:38.041
Hey, honey.

39:38.844 --> 39:40.910
Mornin'.

39:40.912 --> 39:43.046
I need to talk to you
about something,

39:44.549 --> 39:48.651
and you're probably gonna think
it's completely insane.

39:48.653 --> 39:52.288
But I have to tell you.

39:52.290 --> 39:55.058
Well, you know
you can tell me anything.

39:55.060 --> 39:57.394
So just say
what you need to say.

39:58.630 --> 40:01.264
The reason I met with Marybeth

40:02.234 --> 40:04.768
is because she might be
able to bring Mark back.

40:06.605 --> 40:07.771
Bring Mark back?

40:09.374 --> 40:10.907
That's impossible.

40:10.909 --> 40:12.976
I mean, I know
how much you miss him.

40:12.978 --> 40:15.745
Well, I have
to at least try, Dad.

40:15.747 --> 40:19.682
I mean, you know things weren't
supposed to end up like this.

40:19.684 --> 40:22.385
With Marybeth's help,
we could undo some of the damage

40:22.387 --> 40:24.721
- that these people...
- Even if it were possible...

40:27.292 --> 40:30.226
what makes you think it would be
the right thing to do?

40:31.196 --> 40:33.630
It would be disrupting...

40:34.566 --> 40:36.032
Mark's after life.

40:36.034 --> 40:39.068
We'd have to dig him up,
which is illegal.

40:39.070 --> 40:41.471
And not to mention,
it's blasphemous.

40:41.473 --> 40:42.739
I know, Dad.

40:42.741 --> 40:45.175
But I saw Mark on the other side

40:45.177 --> 40:47.644
and he's in terrible pain.

40:47.646 --> 40:48.978
It was a miracle that I'm alive.

40:48.980 --> 40:50.780
You said so yourself.

40:50.782 --> 40:54.117
We just need one more miracle
to set things right again.

40:54.986 --> 40:56.219
If we don't even try,

40:56.221 --> 40:57.720
then what's the fucking point
of all of this?

40:57.722 --> 41:01.191
Just sit on our asses
and wait for them to kill us?

41:01.493 --> 41:02.559
Rebecca?

41:08.934 --> 41:10.233
I'm sorry.

41:13.672 --> 41:15.138
You're all I have left.

41:18.710 --> 41:20.510
I just don't want

41:21.580 --> 41:23.713
someone like Marybeth

41:24.783 --> 41:26.483
to take advantage of you.

41:28.920 --> 41:30.186
You got that?

41:32.157 --> 41:34.324
Do you really need to do this?

41:35.494 --> 41:38.595
Then I'll help you out
however I can, you know.

41:39.998 --> 41:41.397
You know, I'd...

41:42.601 --> 41:44.200
I'd do anything for you.

41:45.437 --> 41:46.436
Thank you, Dad.

42:00.151 --> 42:02.819
Ugh! Oh, oh.

42:04.756 --> 42:06.890
Oh, God.

42:11.663 --> 42:14.297
So much
for the mortician's artistry.

42:16.668 --> 42:18.134
Under no circumstances

42:18.136 --> 42:19.802
should you
interrupt the procedure.

42:20.672 --> 42:23.773
Any interference could
make Mark vulnerable

42:23.775 --> 42:25.308
to dark forces.

42:26.778 --> 42:28.011
Dark forces?

42:28.013 --> 42:30.146
You might know them
as familiar spirits,

42:30.148 --> 42:31.881
as they're referred to
in the Bible.

42:33.451 --> 42:35.585
This should keep them at bay.

42:53.605 --> 42:54.637
Let us begin.

42:58.276 --> 43:01.711
Isis, mother of all,

43:03.348 --> 43:06.449
master of birth,
life and death,

43:06.451 --> 43:07.550
hear us.

43:09.220 --> 43:11.754
You were before time and after,

43:11.756 --> 43:13.623
before knowing and nothing.

43:15.393 --> 43:17.560
Accept the offering, Isis.

43:18.263 --> 43:19.629
Know our prayers.

43:22.767 --> 43:24.534
Accept the offering, Isis.

43:25.704 --> 43:27.604
Let him cross over.

43:29.708 --> 43:31.341
Let him cross over!

43:32.844 --> 43:34.410
Release him, Isis!

43:35.814 --> 43:37.413
Release him!

44:07.278 --> 44:09.379
Son of a bitch.

44:10.682 --> 44:11.914
Mark is alive.

44:13.018 --> 44:14.684
But he's in a catatonic state.

44:15.387 --> 44:17.020
Give him time to rest.

44:17.022 --> 44:20.390
His body needs to recover
from his unnatural resurgence.

44:21.459 --> 44:23.326
Tomorrow he shall awaken anew.

44:24.129 --> 44:26.496
You don't know
what this means to me.

44:26.498 --> 44:27.597
Thank you.

45:01.733 --> 45:03.599
Rest up.

45:03.601 --> 45:05.968
Tomorrow is the first day
of your new life.

45:08.973 --> 45:10.006
Now remember,

45:11.276 --> 45:12.975
you must keep this a secret.

45:12.977 --> 45:16.345
Mark cannot return
to the world he once inhabited.

45:16.347 --> 45:18.448
It would be
too dangerous for him.

45:18.450 --> 45:20.616
Don't worry.
I won't let him out of my sight.

45:20.618 --> 45:22.318
Good.

45:22.320 --> 45:23.953
I brought you
supplies for the weekend.

45:29.160 --> 45:30.827
I'll bring more on Monday.

45:30.829 --> 45:32.628
Just remember
that these will only help

45:32.630 --> 45:34.530
keep evil out of your house.

45:34.532 --> 45:36.265
Henrik's followers
could still come back here

45:36.267 --> 45:37.934
and if they do,
you better call the police.

45:37.936 --> 45:39.736
Oh, don't worry about that.

45:39.738 --> 45:42.538
Sheriff's very sympathetic
of our situation.

45:43.341 --> 45:44.607
Happy to hear that.

46:00.225 --> 46:01.624
Did Henrik's cult specify

46:01.626 --> 46:03.760
why your land
is so important to them?

46:04.395 --> 46:07.563
No, he was very vague about it.

46:07.565 --> 46:10.466
Do you know if there's anything
buried beneath your garage?

46:10.468 --> 46:13.836
There was a hidden
old well during construction.

46:16.074 --> 46:17.173
It's been sealed off and buried

46:17.175 --> 46:20.276
for what looked like centuries.

46:20.278 --> 46:22.211
So we didn't think
it was that important,

46:22.213 --> 46:23.780
so we just covered it up.

46:23.782 --> 46:25.548
Oh, my God, Dad,

46:25.550 --> 46:27.283
there could be
something really horrible

46:27.285 --> 46:28.317
buried down there

46:28.319 --> 46:30.186
and all this time,
we had no idea?

46:30.188 --> 46:31.387
I gotta go.

46:33.958 --> 46:36.526
No matter what happens,
do not let them near that well.

46:38.263 --> 46:39.662
We won't.

46:39.664 --> 46:41.497
Thank you
for everything, Marybeth.

46:41.499 --> 46:43.533
You can thank me
by protecting that well.

46:43.535 --> 46:44.967
Take care of Mark for me.

46:46.104 --> 46:47.103
Good night.

47:50.468 --> 47:52.768
- You want some...
- Yes, sir.

47:59.911 --> 48:01.844
Uh, Mark?

48:03.681 --> 48:04.614
Mark.

48:06.751 --> 48:08.484
- I'm really here.
- Yeah.

48:12.357 --> 48:13.856
Rebecca.

48:24.402 --> 48:26.869
I wish we could just leave
and never come back.

48:26.871 --> 48:29.605
And then maybe they'd
just leave us alone.

48:29.607 --> 48:32.041
No, they'll come find us.

48:32.043 --> 48:34.043
We know too much.

48:34.045 --> 48:38.547
Rebecca, I promise you, if they
come back here, I'll kill them all.

48:38.549 --> 48:39.949
I'm not afraid of them.

48:40.485 --> 48:41.951
I'm not afraid to die.

48:42.854 --> 48:45.955
I promise you,
I will do anything I can

48:45.957 --> 48:47.123
to keep you safe.

48:49.327 --> 48:51.093
Oh shit, it's the Sheriff.

48:53.965 --> 48:56.432
Dad, the sheriff's here.

48:56.434 --> 48:57.767
Come on.

48:59.337 --> 49:01.971
You stay in there and be quiet.

49:11.516 --> 49:12.682
Hey, John.

49:12.917 --> 49:13.983
Jacob.

49:13.985 --> 49:15.785
What's going on?

49:15.787 --> 49:18.054
Someone stole the body
from the cemetery.

49:18.056 --> 49:18.988
Mark's body.

49:18.990 --> 49:21.257
Oh, my God.

49:21.259 --> 49:23.259
Mind if I come inside
and sit down for a moment?

49:24.629 --> 49:26.329
Oh, no, of course not.

49:26.331 --> 49:27.330
Come on

49:29.534 --> 49:30.766
Have a seat.

49:33.171 --> 49:34.370
Jacob.

49:34.372 --> 49:35.871
I think the people
that took Mark's body

49:35.873 --> 49:37.974
are the same people
that have been harassing you.

49:38.743 --> 49:41.677
That Aksel and Henrik Brandr...

49:41.679 --> 49:43.546
Well, have you found
anything on him?

49:43.548 --> 49:45.114
Nothing we could
use against them.

49:45.750 --> 49:46.983
No criminal record.

49:46.985 --> 49:49.819
No lawsuits. They're completely
under the radar.

49:50.521 --> 49:52.588
Look, I can't prove it, yet.

49:52.590 --> 49:54.190
But I know they're responsible

49:54.192 --> 49:57.393
for these damn tragedies,
my families and probably

49:57.395 --> 49:59.061
your other problems, too.

50:00.732 --> 50:02.264
I'm starting to believe you.

50:02.266 --> 50:03.899
Well, that's good.

50:03.901 --> 50:06.702
We haven't had so much as a traffic
violation these past few years.

50:07.538 --> 50:10.206
Ever since that
Aksel visited you,

50:10.208 --> 50:12.174
I got two girls go missing.

50:12.176 --> 50:16.045
And with your family's tragedies
and his body snatching,

50:16.047 --> 50:20.216
it's just... the coincidence
is too big to ignore.

50:21.285 --> 50:22.518
What about the cemetery?

50:22.520 --> 50:25.755
Did you find any evidence?

50:26.424 --> 50:27.790
Nothing we can pin on them.

50:28.760 --> 50:31.060
Had to make sure not to leave
anything behind.

50:34.465 --> 50:37.366
Well, just let me know if
there's anything we can do to...

50:37.368 --> 50:39.035
Listen, uh...

50:39.037 --> 50:40.036
I gotta head out.

50:42.907 --> 50:44.807
Please tell Rebecca
I said hello.

50:44.809 --> 50:45.941
Okay.

50:52.216 --> 50:54.984
It's stressful.
You're supposed to be dead.

50:56.854 --> 50:58.354
Yeah, that was close.

51:00.691 --> 51:02.858
I can't believe
you did this for me.

51:04.662 --> 51:06.762
Must have cost a fortune
for you to save me.

51:07.565 --> 51:09.832
Yeah, it costs
an arm and a leg.

51:10.601 --> 51:12.768
- Mm-hmm.
- No offense.

51:13.204 --> 51:14.837
None taken.

51:17.075 --> 51:20.342
Are you sure you're not
weirded out by me being back?

51:24.582 --> 51:26.749
Mark, I will always love you.

51:27.752 --> 51:29.418
No matter what.

51:30.988 --> 51:32.254
I promise.

51:44.168 --> 51:46.435
Oh, I've missed you.

51:59.650 --> 52:02.151
I'm still getting used to this.

52:02.153 --> 52:04.753
- Looks kind of like chewed up bubble gum.
- Yeah.

52:04.755 --> 52:06.288
Does it hurt?

52:06.290 --> 52:08.424
I don't feel a thing. It's uh...

52:08.426 --> 52:09.859
No, it doesn't hurt at all.

52:09.861 --> 52:11.627
It's almost like it's magic.

52:12.763 --> 52:15.030
Exactly.

52:15.032 --> 52:19.535
Speaking of magic, I'm really
getting attached to this blade

52:19.537 --> 52:21.337
you got me.
That's a pretty serious.

52:22.006 --> 52:22.872
Oh, my God.

52:22.874 --> 52:24.907
That's from Marybeth.

52:24.909 --> 52:26.742
What the hell was that?

52:27.545 --> 52:29.411
I'll find out. Stay here, okay.

52:35.586 --> 52:36.719
What the hell is wrong?

52:36.721 --> 52:37.887
Well, shit, they're here.

52:37.889 --> 52:40.055
Look, call the Sheriff.
Stay with Rebecca.

52:40.057 --> 52:42.158
- Mark, stay with her.
- I will.

52:42.160 --> 52:45.494
Those bastards have fucked
with us for the last time.

52:45.496 --> 52:46.962
Be careful.

52:55.506 --> 52:57.173
Rebecca, we're here to help.

52:57.175 --> 53:00.910
We want to believe you,
but we need to know the truth.

53:00.912 --> 53:02.311
What happened at the cemetery?

53:03.181 --> 53:06.549
We just, we went to visit
Mark's grave.

53:06.551 --> 53:09.185
We said a prayer
and then we left.

53:09.187 --> 53:10.853
That was it.

53:10.855 --> 53:13.522
- Aren't you forgetting something?
- Oh, shit.

53:13.524 --> 53:15.891
What do we do, sir?
He might be a fucking zombie.

53:15.893 --> 53:17.326
Lower your weapons.

53:17.895 --> 53:19.395
What's going on here?

53:19.397 --> 53:20.663
Mark, what the fuck!

53:20.665 --> 53:22.431
Sorry, but I can't stay
locked up forever.

53:22.433 --> 53:24.133
Especially a time like this.

53:35.947 --> 53:38.247
I don't want
to freak you guys out anymore.

53:38.249 --> 53:41.584
But I figured
if anything gets too crazy...

53:42.820 --> 53:44.286
We could use these.

53:44.288 --> 53:46.789
Johnson, what the hell
are you doing with dynamite?

53:46.791 --> 53:48.157
My dad worked in demolition.

53:48.159 --> 53:50.092
I just figured these might
come in handy.

53:50.094 --> 53:52.328
You know, if anything
gets too crazy.

53:52.330 --> 53:56.165
Put that shit down.
One bullet hits that bag, we're all dead.

53:56.167 --> 53:57.333
Yes, sir.

53:57.335 --> 53:58.500
I'll hide him under here

54:19.290 --> 54:20.456
Oh, fuck.

54:20.458 --> 54:21.557
Adams, call for backup.

54:25.963 --> 54:26.962
I can't get a signal, sir.

54:26.964 --> 54:28.197
It's all fucked up.

54:29.133 --> 54:30.366
Rebecca...

54:31.168 --> 54:32.534
Rebecca...

54:37.475 --> 54:38.607
We don't have time to waste.

54:38.609 --> 54:41.610
We should split up. Two people
on each side of the house.

54:41.612 --> 54:43.746
Don't let anyone in the garage.

54:43.748 --> 54:45.881
Adams, you stay with me.
Give Mark your radio.

54:45.883 --> 54:47.516
Everyone, be careful.

54:51.289 --> 54:52.588
Let's go.

54:52.590 --> 54:53.622
We'll take the West.

54:56.894 --> 54:58.527
Don't be afraid.

54:58.529 --> 55:00.596
Satan himself is with us.

55:01.432 --> 55:02.965
Prepare to attack.

55:05.236 --> 55:06.235
Go.

55:12.943 --> 55:15.577
<i>I think I saw
something by the trees. East side.</i>

55:19.817 --> 55:21.116
Oh, shit!

55:21.118 --> 55:22.084
Adams!

55:24.322 --> 55:25.354
Adams is dead.

55:25.356 --> 55:26.622
Shoot to kill

55:26.624 --> 55:28.357
Come on, bloodsuckers!

55:34.231 --> 55:35.831
<i>Don't forget
about my bag.</i>

55:35.833 --> 55:37.633
