your little shopping mall world.

57:40.324 --> 57:45.694
Because you and your kind...

57:46.864 --> 57:50.132
Have ruined everything

57:50.134 --> 57:52.468
that was beautiful
in this world.

57:55.606 --> 57:56.738
But your time's come.

57:57.908 --> 57:59.107
That's right.

57:59.877 --> 58:02.277
Your time has come.

58:02.279 --> 58:05.180
Atone for your sins.

58:11.555 --> 58:12.754
Do you hear that?

58:13.958 --> 58:15.858
Do you hear that?

58:20.164 --> 58:21.530
They're ready for you.

58:24.168 --> 58:25.701
Now, you're just complying.

58:28.606 --> 58:29.872
If you wanna die

58:29.874 --> 58:32.641
with a semblance
of fucking dignity...

58:44.688 --> 58:46.188
Am gonna cut off

58:46.190 --> 58:50.692
your fucking tits
and shovel up, you motherfuck.

59:30.701 --> 59:32.200
Holy shit.

59:32.202 --> 59:34.469
How's that for dignity,
fuck face?

59:35.105 --> 59:36.538
Thank God you're all right.

59:46.884 --> 59:49.117
- Are you okay?
- Yeah, yeah.

59:49.119 --> 59:51.253
- Yeah.
- Thank you.

59:51.255 --> 59:53.055
We have to get out of here. Now.

59:53.057 --> 59:54.222
Rebecca, go with Marybeth.

59:54.224 --> 59:55.857
No, I'm not leaving you.

59:55.859 --> 59:56.858
I can't lose you.

59:57.461 --> 59:58.360
Go.

59:58.362 --> 1:00:00.195
Whatever is down there
must be stopped.

1:00:00.197 --> 1:00:01.630
I'll put an end to this.

1:00:01.632 --> 1:00:03.899
- Mark, don't leave me.
- No, he is right.

1:00:03.901 --> 1:00:05.434
If we stay here,
we're gonna perish.

1:00:05.436 --> 1:00:07.235
Everything you've been through
will be in vain.

1:00:07.237 --> 1:00:08.804
Mark, you can't do this.

1:00:08.806 --> 1:00:10.439
I have to do this.

1:00:10.441 --> 1:00:13.308
Please, let me honor the life
that you have given me.

1:00:13.711 --> 1:00:14.710
Go.

1:00:15.913 --> 1:00:16.878
Go.

1:00:20.317 --> 1:00:22.317
Don't you die again.

1:00:25.856 --> 1:00:26.855
Now go...

1:00:26.857 --> 1:00:27.990
Go.

1:00:28.792 --> 1:00:30.459
Please... go.

1:00:32.196 --> 1:00:33.462
