1:01:11.268 --> 1:01:12.968
Please don't let me
screw this up.

1:01:15.305 --> 1:01:17.472
Please let me see Rebecca again.

1:01:43.233 --> 1:01:47.335
Satan,
please accept this offering.

1:01:47.337 --> 1:01:50.572
May it nourish
your sleeping child.

1:01:51.975 --> 1:01:55.410
