1:02:05.956 --> 1:02:07.589
We mustn't lose the child!

1:02:07.591 --> 1:02:08.924
Fuck you!

1:02:19.670 --> 1:02:21.503
Damn you, Mark!

1:02:21.505 --> 1:02:26.041
Curse you and your family
by the power of Satan himself!

1:02:26.043 --> 1:02:27.943
