Please... Awake... Please.

1:03:08.786 --> 1:03:10.152
I beg of you.

1:03:11.255 --> 1:03:14.156
Don't let our suffering
be in vain.

1:03:15.192 --> 1:03:16.792
We've served you well.

1:03:17.995 --> 1:03:21.730
Arise... Arise, I command you.

1:03:43.921 --> 1:03:45.554
Oh, thank you, Father.

1:03:45.556 --> 1:03:47.923
Thank you for hearing my cries.

1:03:50.360 --> 1:03:53.061
Thank you for accepting
our offerings.

1:03:55.098 --> 1:03:59.801
Please let me serve you.

1:03:59.803 --> 1:04:04.673
I humbly beg to be your servant
for the rest of my life.

1:05:21.151 --> 1:05:22.517
Thank you.

1:05:34.464 --> 1:05:35.563
Oh, yeah.

1:05:35.565 --> 1:05:37.999
I mean, I pointed it
right at his head,

1:05:38.001 --> 1:05:43.705
and his brain just turned into
this bloody oatmeal like mush.

1:05:43.707 --> 1:05:46.174
It came out of every orifice
in his head.

1:05:47.044 --> 1:05:48.576
It was insane.

1:05:48.578 --> 1:05:50.312
<i>Oh, my God. That is insane.</i>

1:05:50.314 --> 1:05:53.648
<i>I can honestly say I've never heard
of that one being done before.</i>

1:05:53.650 --> 1:05:55.216
<i>So it worked pretty well then.</i>

1:05:55.218 --> 1:05:58.219
Oh. It was so effective
and fast.

1:05:58.221 --> 1:06:00.255
It was just so messy.

1:06:01.291 --> 1:06:02.824
<i>I'm sorry.
I don't mean to laugh.</i>

1:06:02.826 --> 1:06:05.226
<i>It's just this whole thing.
