1:06:19.209 --> 1:06:21.309
<i>Just glad you're all okay.
That's the thing.</i>

1:06:21.311 --> 1:06:22.577
Good morning.

1:06:22.980 --> 1:06:24.145
- Hey.
- Hey.

1:06:26.016 --> 1:06:27.382
<i>So, is Mark still...</i>

1:06:27.384 --> 1:06:29.084
