1:06:29.086 --> 1:06:29.918
I gotta go.

1:06:29.920 --> 1:06:32.120
<i>Okay.
I'll talk to you later then.</i>

1:06:32.122 --> 1:06:33.054
<i>Goodbye, Rebecca.</i>

1:06:33.056 --> 1:06:35.623
- <i>Say hello to Mark for me.</i>
- Bye.

1:06:37.461 --> 1:06:39.894
I see somebody is awake.

1:06:42.366 --> 1:06:45.000
How do you feel?

1:06:45.002 --> 1:06:47.102
Like I have
a hangover from hell.

1:06:48.739 --> 1:06:52.307
Next time, just let me die
for fuck's sake.

1:06:52.309 --> 1:06:53.742
