1:06:53.744 --> 1:06:56.144
So you're just gonna have
to suck it up.

1:06:56.513 --> 1:06:57.712
Mark?

1:06:58.982 --> 1:06:59.981
Is it all over?

1:07:00.751 --> 1:07:03.752
Whatever was down there is dead.

1:07:03.754 --> 1:07:06.121
Along with the rest
of its adoring fan base.

1:07:06.690 --> 1:07:08.189
Boom all straight to hell.

1:07:11.728 --> 1:07:13.328
I will need to read your hands.

1:07:14.998 --> 1:07:18.033
We have to make sure
the curse has been lifted.
